<br>
Windblade for DPS, ToD for slow<br>
Fungi<br>
8th Ring<br>
Eyepatch of Plunder + CoF<br>
Embalmers Skinning Knife<br>
Snare whip (paired with frosty for decent dmg while snaring)<br>
Jboots<br>
Lodi &amp; Cobalt Boots, Cobalt Arms.<br>
Incarnadine BP<br>
<br>
HP and ac, self buffed, are in the 3100/1100 range respectively.<br>
<br>
Can't think of much more gear I can get to help soloing (although I'm not far off 9th ring which should provide some nice extra HP and save me swapping the ring out on those rare occasions I need to click it).  A thurg or cobalt BP would be nice for the heals, but they're reasonably pricey.<br>
<br>
The one thing I'm missing is a place to solo.  At 54 it seems that a whole pile of stuff goes light blue.  I can do forgotten slaves in the Grey, which are nice xp and which can't stand up to him at all, but they are too tricky to pull consistantly.  Too many rockfiends/wurms adding.<br>
<br>
Does anyone have any suggestions on where to go to XP my trollie?  I havn't got PoP yet (it's still not out in New Zealand!) but I understand that when it arrives, I'll get better xp grouping in the planes than I ever could soloing… your thoughts on that would be appreciated, too.<br>
